155
00:11:44,463 --> 00:11:51,465
In 2003, an antiquities dealer in the United States bought it and then created a fake ownership

156
00:11:51,565 --> 00:11:55,046
history for the tablet before selling it on.

157
00:11:56,487 --> 00:12:02,169
The tablet changed hands many times before ultimately ending up in a museum, not the

158
00:12:02,229 --> 00:12:06,510
Smithsonian, not far from where Catherine and I work in Washington, D.C.

159
00:12:08,819 --> 00:12:11,741
So this is where the Cultural Antiquities Task Force comes in.

160
00:12:13,043 --> 00:12:15,565
Since 2004, the Cultural Antiquities Task Force

161
00:12:15,945 --> 00:12:18,668
has coordinated with federal law enforcement agencies,

162
00:12:19,168 --> 00:12:23,352
foreign partners, and Interpol to disrupt the theft, looting,

163
00:12:23,733 --> 00:12:26,415
vandalism, and trafficking of cultural heritage.

164
00:12:28,332 --> 00:12:35,217
Organized crime syndicates, including terrorists, steal, loot, and illegally export objects

165
00:12:35,557 --> 00:12:41,641
like the Gilgamesh Dream tablet and sell these national treasures to dealers and collectors

166
00:12:41,901 --> 00:12:42,541
