168
00:12:51,086 --> 00:12:57,387
sometimes destroying whole sites in the process and thus depriving us of vital information

169
00:12:57,768 --> 00:13:03,069
for understanding past societies, which then goes on to inspire all of our gamers.

170
00:13:04,729 --> 00:13:10,831
Often the trafficked objects find their way into private collections, never to be seen

171
00:13:10,891 --> 00:13:11,091
